//   3. No agent declares the capability → NOT_FOUND (with a machine-readable
//      reason in the status message).
//   4. Candidates exist but hard constraints, readiness, or the expert
//      target eliminate all of them → FAILED_PRECONDITION; the status
//      message names the first eliminating filter.
